name: Portrait of Dora Maar
description: Portrait of Dora Maar (French: Portrait de Dora Maar) is a 1937 oil on canvas painting by Pablo Picasso. It depicts Dora Maar, (original name Henriette Theodora Markovitch), the painter's lover, seated on a chair. It is part of the collection of the Mus√©e Picasso, in Paris, where it is considered to be one of Picasso's masterpieces.
